{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>给出两幅相同大小的黑白图像（用0-1矩阵）表示，求它们的相似度。说明：若两幅图像在相同位置上的像素点颜色相同，则称它们在该位置具有相同的像素点。两幅图像的相似度定义为相同像素点数占总像素点数的百分比。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"图像相似度 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>一个实数，表示相似度（以百分比的形式给出），精确到小数点后两位。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行包含两个整数m和n，表示图像的行数和列数，中间用单个空格隔开。1≤m≤100, 1≤n≤100。<p><p>之后m行，每行n个整数0或1，表示第一幅黑白图像上各像素点的颜色。相邻两个数之间用单个空格隔开。<p><p>之后m行，每行n个整数0或1，表示第二幅黑白图像上各像素点的颜色。相邻两个数之间用单个空格隔开。<p>","examples":"<input>3 3\n1 0 1\n0 0 1\n1 1 0\n1 1 0\n0 0 1\n0 0 1\n\n</input><output>44.44\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1123","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}